{"tid":1977911,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"主[能]夠｜如何改詞｜廣東話歌分析及創作｜","createTime":"2020-04-18T10:07:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-18T10:28:12.000Z","uid":356405,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"743eb2e2a6ad676bb231f5937da064db6a442b5f","tid":1977911,"uid":356405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T10:07:44.000Z","msg":"很多廣東話的舊式詩歌的發音都不正確 <br />\n例如：我愛我個神「腎」 ，主「能」夠<br />\n這影片嘗試分析及改善這個情況<br />\n<br />\n影片有兩個主要內容 <br />\n第一是分析著名的廣東話舊式詩歌 <br />\n看看他們的廣東話發音是如何不正確<br />\n第二是改詞，方法是調動歌詞組合<br />\n嘗試組合一個正確發音及正確意思的版本 <br />\n<br />\n包保唔係垃圾片，一定有野學到<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Y7vwRTGPQ-8&amp;t=5s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DY7vwRTGPQ-8%26t%3D5s&d=0xR7vGHOl893LUq1yoppeo5RPfZ%2FgKFUZzIsJfjgB6g%3D&h=30e6083a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Y7vwRTGPQ-8&amp;t=5s</a>"},{"pid":"efafff5e2b368a65538e6a4524104e3c090106a2","tid":1977911,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T10:28:12.000Z","msg":"人地係要拎返原詩大概意思<br />\n根本就唔係音樂，冇需要啱音，又何來不正確<br />\n<br />\n更何況主能夠係普通話詞嚟，純粹係啲白痴自己無啦啦拎嚟用廣東話唱<br />\n<br />\n你用拎錯例子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}